reviewText: Features four scenes, the first is inter-racial as the gals make out, grind and disrobe. Kiss, lick, inhail and slobber . Like muppets they are a bit camera-shy as there appears to be nothing there below the waist. Next are the covergirls a well-endowed blond and brunette. #3 features a pretty girl with short hair, they stand up the whole time. The final pair is two brunettes. At times the couples do not seem to know what to do next. Virtually no talking at all, each scene just concludes. See Blue Is the Warmest Color (Criterion Collection) (Blu-ray) for a bit more. With these the viewer is left to imagine who these people are to each other, if anybody. Perhaps they are strangers. Engaging.
